    <h1 id="what-is-protocol-overlay-fundamentals-and-practical-insights" tabindex="-1">What is protocol overlay? Fundamentals and practical insights</h1>
<p><img src="https://csuxjmfbwmkxiegfpljm.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/blog-images/organization-24002/1775212228804_image.jpeg" alt="Professional reviewing network overlay diagram"></p>
<hr>
